<h2>Default</h2>
{% call field() %}
  {{ label({ for: "slovenija-emso-input-demo", text: "Unique Master Citizen Number" }) }}
  {{ slovenijaEmsoInput({ id: "slovenija-emso-input-demo" }) }}
{% endcall %}

<h2>Format</h2>
<p>13 digits: the first 7 are the date of birth (DDMMYYY), digits 8-9 the register, 10-12 a sex-and-serial component (000-499 male, 500-999 female), 13 a check digit.</p>

<h2>Reference</h2>
<p>See <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Unique_Master_Citizen_Number">Unique Master Citizen Number</a>.</p>
